		h3 Supported Operating Systems
		p.
			At this time, we develop for the most current operating system across platforms. If a project is going to be released to the market, we rely on third-party vendors to take care of compatibility issues. 

		h3 Programming for Supported Devices & Hybrid Apps
		p.
			Because of our existing partnerships, we try to compile for iOS, Androids, and Windows mobile platforms. This is done using the technology of your choice. As of Spring, 2016, the Product team is using #[a(href="https://facebook.github.io/react-native/") React Native], and R&D has explored #[a(href="https://software.intel.com/en-us/intel-xdk") Intel XDK] and is learning React but no platform has been chosen.  
		
